{"tid":1401502,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"雨傘就係衰在捉鬼分化，今次絕對唔可以再分化！","createTime":"2019-08-03T14:51:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T15:10:23.000Z","uid":196450,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6e5996f5ea4ec08d51fd49f9ab145e266ea22035","tid":1401502,"uid":196450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:51:07.000Z","msg":"無論前線再錯，就算真係有鬼都好，絕對唔可以用「屌」既語氣去講！就算講到喊講到心痛講到想死都係要繼續慢慢講，我地最大既本錢係團結，最輸唔起既都係團結呀！<br />\n<br />\n點都好，絕對不能屌！我都好唔認同前線唔走，我都好嬲佢地點解要留，但我就算嬲到爆炸都絕對唔屌！<br />\n<br />\n因為團結係我地唯一同最大既本錢，五年前衰過一次，今次再輸唔起！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今鋪我就算死都絕不割蓆，絕不篤灰，絕不分化！！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1bf1a053f2f6d37e24a6cbe1b16e08a5941a597","tid":1401502,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:05:47.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n有義士俾狗拉 大家心情一定唔好 但語氣唔該克制啲<br />\n粗口留番俾敵人，唔係自己友"},{"pid":"d2c006f293f071bc7c2e4b8817511c0c0fc3e277","tid":1401502,"uid":25606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:06:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"465f221ff6666723eba078c5e46040829c51c7d5","tid":1401502,"uid":79602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:10:23.000Z","msg":"無人帶頭 真係好易比人帶走個風向"}]}